abstract_ssm: The Brooklyn Fox Corporation records are housed in a single bound volume and dated 1937. The papers include certificates of incorporation, court papers, bonds, correspondence, and other documents. The Brooklyn Fox Corporation was a real estate development and management company that specialized in all types of commercial and residential properties, including theaters, hotels, apartment buildings, office buildings, and storefronts.
